description: Stillfront Group AB engages in the developing, publishing, and distributing digital games. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 1,250 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2015-12-08. The firm operates through a number of near-autonomous subsidiaries, including Bytro Labs in Germany, Coldwood Interactive in Sweden, Power Challenge in the United Kingdom and Sweden, and Dorado Online Games in Malta, Simutronics in the United States, and Babil Games in United Arab Emirates and Jordan, among others. The firm's games portfolio includes Call of War, DragonRealms, ManagerZone Football, Lara Croft Relic Run, Supremacy 1914 and Unravel, among others. The games are distributed globally, however the main markets are Sweden, Germany, the United States, United Kingdom, Middle East and North Africa.
name: Stillfront Group AB (publ)
